    <item>
      <title>美国失业救济申请人数降至四个月低点 218,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/us-jobless-claims-slide-to-four-month-low-of-218-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国劳工部周四公布的数据，截至 9 月 21 日当周，美国失业救济申请人数减少 4,000 人，降至 218,000 人，降至四个月以来的最低水平。彭博电视台的 Jonathan Ferro 和 Lisa Abramowicz 为您带来详细报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/us-jobless-claims-slide-to-four-month-low-of-218-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 13:18:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贵金属价格上涨，白银价格飙升至 2012 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/silver-surges-to-the-highest-since-2012-as-precious-metals-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储进一步降息的预期提振了贵金属价格，白银价格触及2012年以来的最高水平，黄金价格也创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/silver-surges-to-the-highest-since-2012-as-precious-metals-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 11:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴斯夫大幅削减股息，考虑将子公司上市，因业绩下滑加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/basf-seeks-overhaul-with-lower-dividend-focus-on-core-units</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为广泛改革的一部分，巴斯夫欧洲公司将削减股息并剥离资产，改革可能涉及关闭更多德国工厂，以应对高昂的能源价格和中国市场的持续低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/basf-seeks-overhaul-with-lower-dividend-focus-on-core-units</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
